-- use existing shipper_rate_date_extended in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVRD41666224287249_shipper_rate_date_extended
-- use existing shipper_rate_date_forecast in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVJQ11666224424672_shipper_rate_date_forecast
-- use existing shipper_rate_forecast_month_agg in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVRFA1666224424676_shipper_rate_forecast_month_agg
-- use existing shipper_rate_last_date in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVQFY1666224424677_shipper_rate_last_date
-- use existing shipments_spot_last_60_days in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV7XD1666224295136_shipments_spot_last_60_days
-- use existing shipments_actual in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV2F51666224385398_shipments_actual
SELECT
    (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('month', shipper_rate_date_extended."ACTUAL_DATE" ), 'YYYY-MM')) AS "shipper_rate_date_extended.date_month",
    COALESCE(SUM(( coalesce((coalesce(shipper_rate_date_forecast.forecasted_volume_accepted_sum, shipper_rate_last_date.forecasted_volume_accepted_sum,0)),0) + coalesce((coalesce(shipments_spot_last_60_days.volume_rolling_90,0)),0)  ) ), 0) AS "shipper_rate_date_extended.volume_forecast",
    COALESCE(SUM(( coalesce((coalesce(shipper_rate_date_forecast.forecasted_revenue_sum, shipper_rate_last_date.forecasted_revenue_sum,0)),0) + coalesce((coalesce(shipments_spot_last_60_days.revenue_rolling_90,0)),0)  ) ), 0) AS "shipper_rate_date_extended.revenue_forecast",
    COALESCE(SUM(( coalesce((coalesce(nullif(shipper_rate_date_forecast.forecasted_margin_sum,0), nullif(shipper_rate_last_date.forecasted_margin_sum,0), nullif((coalesce(shipper_rate_date_forecast.forecasted_revenue_sum, shipper_rate_last_date.forecasted_revenue_sum,0))*(shipper_rate_forecast_month_agg.forecasted_margin_sum/nullif(shipper_rate_forecast_month_agg.forecasted_revenue_sum,0)),0))),0) + coalesce((coalesce(shipments_spot_last_60_days.margin_rolling_90,0)),0)  ) ), 0) AS "shipper_rate_date_extended.margin_forecast",
    COALESCE(CAST( ( SUM(DISTINCT (CAST(FLOOR(COALESCE( shipments_actual.shipment_count ,0)*(1000000*1.0)) AS DECIMAL(38,0))) + (TO_NUMBER(MD5( shipments_actual.finance_record_date_skey  || '-' ||  shipments_actual.shipper_application_id  || '-' ||  shipments_actual.is_drop_trailer  ||  shipments_actual.transfix_lane_id   ), 'XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX') % 1.0e27)::NUMERIC(38, 0) ) - SUM(DISTINCT (TO_NUMBER(MD5( shipments_actual.finance_record_date_skey  || '-' ||  shipments_actual.shipper_application_id  || '-' ||  shipments_actual.is_drop_trailer  ||  shipments_actual.transfix_lane_id   ), 'XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX') % 1.0e27)::NUMERIC(38, 0)) )  AS DOUBLE PRECISION) / CAST((1000000*1.0) AS DOUBLE PRECISION), 0) AS "shipments_actual.volume",
    COALESCE(CAST( ( SUM(DISTINCT (CAST(FLOOR(COALESCE( shipments_actual.total_revenue_sum ,0)*(1000000*1.0)) AS DECIMAL(38,0))) + (TO_NUMBER(MD5( shipments_actual.finance_record_date_skey  || '-' ||  shipments_actual.shipper_application_id  || '-' ||  shipments_actual.is_drop_trailer  ||  shipments_actual.transfix_lane_id   ), 'XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX') % 1.0e27)::NUMERIC(38, 0) ) - SUM(DISTINCT (TO_NUMBER(MD5( shipments_actual.finance_record_date_skey  || '-' ||  shipments_actual.shipper_application_id  || '-' ||  shipments_actual.is_drop_trailer  ||  shipments_actual.transfix_lane_id   ), 'XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX') % 1.0e27)::NUMERIC(38, 0)) )  AS DOUBLE PRECISION) / CAST((1000000*1.0) AS DOUBLE PRECISION), 0) AS "shipments_actual.revenue",
    COALESCE(CAST( ( SUM(DISTINCT (CAST(FLOOR(COALESCE( shipments_actual.total_margin_sum ,0)*(1000000*1.0)) AS DECIMAL(38,0))) + (TO_NUMBER(MD5( shipments_actual.finance_record_date_skey  || '-' ||  shipments_actual.shipper_application_id  || '-' ||  shipments_actual.is_drop_trailer  ||  shipments_actual.transfix_lane_id   ), 'XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX') % 1.0e27)::NUMERIC(38, 0) ) - SUM(DISTINCT (TO_NUMBER(MD5( shipments_actual.finance_record_date_skey  || '-' ||  shipments_actual.shipper_application_id  || '-' ||  shipments_actual.is_drop_trailer  ||  shipments_actual.transfix_lane_id   ), 'XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX') % 1.0e27)::NUMERIC(38, 0)) )  AS DOUBLE PRECISION) / CAST((1000000*1.0) AS DOUBLE PRECISION), 0) AS "shipments_actual.margin"
FROM LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVRD41666224287249_shipper_rate_date_extended AS shipper_rate_date_extended
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVJQ11666224424672_shipper_rate_date_forecast AS shipper_rate_date_forecast ON shipper_rate_date_forecast.id = (shipper_rate_date_extended."SHIPPER_RATE_ID") and shipper_rate_date_forecast.date_skey = shipper_rate_date_extended.date_skey
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVRFA1666224424676_shipper_rate_forecast_month_agg AS shipper_rate_forecast_month_agg ON (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('month', shipper_rate_forecast_month_agg.date_month), 'YYYY-MM')) = (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('month', shipper_rate_date_extended."ACTUAL_DATE" ), 'YYYY-MM'))
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVQFY1666224424677_shipper_rate_last_date AS shipper_rate_last_date ON shipper_rate_last_date.id = (shipper_rate_date_extended."SHIPPER_RATE_ID") and shipper_rate_date_extended.date_skey > shipper_rate_last_date.date_skey and shipper_rate_last_date.is_last_business_day and shipper_rate_last_date.is_latest_network_rfp
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV7XD1666224295136_shipments_spot_last_60_days AS shipments_spot_last_60_days ON shipments_spot_last_60_days.date_skey = shipper_rate_date_extended.date_skey and
      shipments_spot_last_60_days.shipper_application_id = (shipper_rate_date_extended."SHIPPER_APPLICATION_ID") and
      shipments_spot_last_60_days.transfix_lane_id = (shipper_rate_date_extended."TRANSFIX_LANE_ID") and
      shipments_spot_last_60_days.is_drop_trailer = (shipper_rate_date_extended."IS_DROP_TRAILER") and
      shipments_spot_last_60_days.equipment_parent_id = (shipper_rate_date_extended."EQUIPMENT_PARENT_ID") and
      (shipper_rate_date_extended."SHIPPER_RATE_ID") = 0

LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV2F51666224385398_shipments_actual AS shipments_actual ON shipments_actual.finance_record_date_skey = shipper_rate_date_extended.date_skey and
      shipments_actual.shipper_application_id = (shipper_rate_date_extended."SHIPPER_APPLICATION_ID") and
      shipments_actual.transfix_lane_id = (shipper_rate_date_extended."TRANSFIX_LANE_ID") and
      shipments_actual.is_drop_trailer = (shipper_rate_date_extended."IS_DROP_TRAILER")
WHERE ((( shipper_rate_date_extended."ACTUAL_DATE"  ) >= ((DATEADD('month', -6, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))))) AND ( shipper_rate_date_extended."ACTUAL_DATE"  ) < ((DATEADD('month', 7, DATEADD('month', -6, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))))))))
GROUP BY
    (DATE_TRUNC('month', shipper_rate_date_extended."ACTUAL_DATE" ))
ORDER BY
    1 DESC
FETCH NEXT 500 ROWS ONLY
